Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，找沙维图迪先生，是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不认识他？什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，正是，我是他的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我从西西里打来，打了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我懂了，他不在那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可否请你告诉我电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}656-22-056，谢谢，再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}妈妈，打电话没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他很忙，到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他不会记得的，这件事算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他已30年没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你知道哥哥的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他会记得的，我相信他会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我比你了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果他事后才知道我们没告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他一定会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}请找沙维图迪维多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是他的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有什么好看的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图迪，几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}很晚了，很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没法让你知道，晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你妈来电，她以为我是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我顺她意，不想令她失望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谈了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她说你有三十年没去看她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她想见你时，会来罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她来电只为了说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不，她说有人死了，叫艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}明天出殡，他是谁？亲戚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不是，睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}世人都被邪恶困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“仅以这杯圣血…”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“请您…”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“请您…”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“请您赦免世人所犯的罪行”阿门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}告诉你多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有铃声我会忘词，只知道睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你晚上都在干嘛，吃东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}神父，我家半夜不吃东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是兽医这么交代，所以我很疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我知道你为何疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别以为我不知道，回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我有事要做，快滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我能留下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，出去！你不能留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我想留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可以开始放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}将画面调好，一天到晚只知道睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs22\bord0\shad7\4a&H78&\1c&H9E9E9E&}《低下层》 首映日期: 1936年12月03日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn迷你简超粗黑\fs36\bord0\shad10\3a&H64&\4a&H7D&\pos(198,235)\1c&H959595&}主演  让・迦本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn迷你简超粗黑\fs36\bord0\shad10\3a&H64&\4a&H7D&\pos(198,235)\1c&H959595&}导演  让・雷诺阿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}鲍比，有一天我们会拥有它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们远走高飞，过舒适生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有人认识我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不再爱我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}1双，2双，100里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}纯尼龙袜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不能来这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我告诉你多少遍，你却当耳边风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}万一胶卷着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}像你这样的小鬼是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}轰的一声…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然后变成一堆炭灰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你喜欢耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一天我要把你舌头剪掉，像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可以给我吗？可不可以给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不可以！我得在还影片前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}把它接回去，你这个小坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为什么不把这些胶卷都接回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我有些找不到正确位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就搁在这里，反正啊，吻戏太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可以给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不行，过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在我踢你屁股前，我们做个交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这些是送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但是，一、你快滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}二、它们留在这里，懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好，一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这算什么交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果是我的，何必留在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不准再来，否则揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“先发射，再思考”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“软弱不忠的狗不中用”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“肮脏猪，不准碰金子”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“黑心猪，别来烦我”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“否则打烂你的头”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}妈妈，战争结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}爸爸为何不回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他会回来的，总有一天会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我已不记得他的样子了，俄国在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要花好几年去，好几年回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上床吧，很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快走！你骗得了你妈，但骗不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}给我拿到文凭好当警察，懒骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别耍花招，进去上课，否则你死定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}赶快走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}5X5=多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}30
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静，背九九乘法表的5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}1乘5得5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}2乘5得10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}3乘5得15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}4乘5得20
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}5乘5等于多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}40
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}波其亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}25
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}背好乘法表，否则找不到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再问一次，5乘5得多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是付钱进来的，我在看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}下来，小捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要讲多少次，回座位去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}比野兔还调皮，到处都是小怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要去奥勒岗，在牧场等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}等一个死人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs22\bord0\shad7\4a&H78&\1c&H9E9E9E&}《关山飞渡》 首映日期：1939年02月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}大家好，我不能打招呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}今天有两个主角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我来这睡觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你都抽什么烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}美国牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，切掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“抵抗运动纪念集会”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有重大新闻发生，请各位安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}意大利将不会忘记“抵抗运动”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那些在秘密中战斗的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}英勇的游击队在罗马重新组合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}成立第一次抵抗运动…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}欢迎，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喔，你这个迟到的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs22\bord0\shad7\4a&H78&\1c&H9E9E9E&}《大地在波动》 首映日期:1948年08月18日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn迷你简粗宋\fs26\bord0\shad0\4a&HFF&\pos(198,220)\1c&H9E9E9E&}主演：西西里的渔民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn迷你简粗宋\fs26\bord0\shad0\4a&HFF&\pos(198,220)\1c&H9E9E9E&}导演：维斯康堤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上头写什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我又不识字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你也是？是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}意大利文不是西西里岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}低下阶层的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们整日辛劳工作12小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}仅换取微薄食物以免于饥饿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然而他们撒下的网
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一旦拉起，必是丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“每次仅有7，750里拉”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就这么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所赚的总是被那些混蛋诈取
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}从以前就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}其他村里也都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}20年前每看电影，没一次有吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}何时才有？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs22\bord0\shad4\4a&H78&\1c&HC0C0C0&}《击倒》 首映时间：1914年06月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没水准！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你和你去工作，我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}去找史达林要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他就要发了，你等着瞧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每次都没挑我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}电影真棒，他们演得好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真可惜他这么倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}去买那艘船是坏主意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}白痴，你一点也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}各位，你们将从清晨工作到黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且不准问工资多少
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.28,0:24:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我等了一整天，牛奶买了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.85,0:24:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}钱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.49,0:25:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你拿去看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}电影，你除了看电影还会做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.00,0:25:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么了？玛莉亚太太
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别打了，别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为何老是说谎？你是免费进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.74,0:25:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}告诉你妈，钱可能是在里头搞丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.19,0:25:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}50里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.36,0:25:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你今晚在椅子下找到些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}梳子，鞋跟皮，烟草罐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:26:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}和50里拉，看到没？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.76,0:26:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢你，艾佛特，晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.14,0:26:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我一下子就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.94,0:26:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}广场是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.78,0:26:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}午夜了，出去！我得关闭广场了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.41,0:28:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}脚痛吗？神父
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.01,0:28:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}去时下坡路，圣者皆助我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.48,0:28:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}回时上坡路，圣者一旁看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.05,0:28:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}大概是上帝之旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.39,0:28:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.49,0:28:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么搞的，轮到你脚痛了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老是出状况，怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，你可认识我爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.01,0:28:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好问题，我认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.61,0:28:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}瘦高，开朗，和我一样留帅胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}总是挂着笑容，如克拉克盖博
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.19,0:28:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特…说下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.96,0:28:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你说我长大了要升5年级
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.09,0:29:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我并不是要说求你让我到放映室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.30,0:29:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过我们总该可以做个朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.43,0:29:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我以外表选朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}以智慧选敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你太狡猾，不能做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我常告诉我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.08,0:29:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不要交友不慎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.58,0:29:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你又没孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.09,0:29:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我若有，将会告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.99,0:29:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别哭…没事了，火灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.23,0:29:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}妈妈在这，乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.67,0:29:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.47,0:29:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}混蛋！你妹差点烧死，全是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.38,0:29:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}叫你别把胶卷放在火盆旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.02,0:29:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}连照片也烧掉了…差点烧掉房子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.00,0:30:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么鬼电影，都长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.21,0:30:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还像个小孩子，真丢人！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.15,0:30:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为何看我？我什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谁给他胶卷的？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.75,0:30:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别再给他，他快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.82,0:30:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他满嘴的电影，电影…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.32,0:30:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再这样下去会害了他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.83,0:30:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}发誓你不再让他进去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.07,0:30:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上帝会派你爸回来鞭打你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:31:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}爸不会回来，我知道原因，他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.38,0:31:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不是真的，你会看到他回来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.08,0:31:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs10\bord0\shad4\4a&H78&\pos(197,160)\frz359\1c&HC0C0C0&}《以法之名》 首映日期：1949年02月19日
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.15,0:31:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真理是永远不变的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}时间像流水般的流着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.18,0:32:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}都是一些老烟枪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.22,0:32:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不行，去买票
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.85,0:32:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谁干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.78,0:32:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要把你们剁成肉酱，你们等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安娜太太
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.22,0:33:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，别骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.33,0:33:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你太太叫我拿饭盒给你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.23,0:33:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.36,0:33:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我告诉我妈，胶卷不是你给的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.70,0:33:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.87,0:33:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我以为胶卷着火是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.41,0:33:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我来这是告诉你这些，我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.38,0:33:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，过来，过来坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:34:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听着，我从十岁就开始干这一行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.56,0:34:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那时，机器还没如此进步
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.03,0:34:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}放映的是默片
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.67,0:34:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且得用手摇放映机的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.04,0:34:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}摇柄摇一整天，那摇柄难得很
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.98,0:34:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}万一你累了，稍为摇慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.95,0:34:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}轰的一声就着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.06,0:34:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你为什么不教我？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.56,0:34:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在不用摇柄简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.06,0:34:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}因为我不想教，这工作不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.40,0:34:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}它教人像个孤单的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.77,0:34:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一副胶卷看上百遍，没其他事可做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.44,0:34:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}像只笨马和嘉易泰伦包尔说话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也像驴子般的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.92,0:34:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}连复活节，圣诞节等假日都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.82,0:35:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只有星期五放假
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.36,0:35:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且万一碰到跟基督有关的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.49,0:35:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还得工作
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.56,0:35:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为什么不换工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.51,0:35:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}因为我是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.51,0:35:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}镇上还有谁会放映电影？没有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.48,0:35:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只有我这个白痴，我从来没走运过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.66,0:35:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}小时候生长在战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.36,0:35:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在长大了仍是活在战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.37,0:35:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你还想干我这没出息的行业？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.67,0:35:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不想
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.97,0:35:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要得！多多，我告诉你是为你好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.51,0:36:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}待在这里，夏天闷热，冬天寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还要忍受烟熏，且赚的仅可糊口
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.06,0:36:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那你还喜欢这种工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.39,0:36:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是渐渐喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.36,0:36:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听到满屋子人们谈笑嬉闹的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.90,0:36:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}自己也跟着快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.00,0:36:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听到他们的声音令我愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.11,0:36:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}仿佛自己是制造快乐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.41,0:36:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}令他们忘记烦恼，我喜欢是这部份
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.08,0:36:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我说的你可能听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你在干什么，多多
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.76,0:36:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}假装在听，却在耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.50,0:36:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你妈说的对，你这鬼灵精
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.94,0:37:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他是怎么会的，边看边学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.48,0:37:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多！你给我听着
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.45,0:37:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要叫管理员不让你进来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.49,0:37:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我还要找阿德菲神父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}叫他别让你当小祭司
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.52,0:37:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}中奖了…我中足球彩卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.48,0:37:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那不勒斯人中彩卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那不勒斯来的奇奇欧中彩卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.59,0:37:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}北方人手气总是比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.76,0:38:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}广场是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.20,0:38:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别动，马蝇会叮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.51,0:38:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这里快变成跳瘙工厂了，快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.99,0:39:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看什么看，滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.97,0:39:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一个商人有两家商店
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}其中一家卖水果…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.75,0:39:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.99,0:39:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.22,0:39:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}旁听学生要参加考试拿文凭
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.24,0:39:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.40,0:41:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，忘恩负义的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.15,0:41:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，帮个忙，安静
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.75,0:41:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我算不来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.72,0:41:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.77,0:42:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“弗南斯哥马沙那，你被捕了”
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.81,0:43:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}干掉那讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.86,0:43:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}混账东西，你给我记住！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.16,0:43:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这里最容易起火
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.86,0:43:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}万一着火了，关掉这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.07,0:43:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}否则整台机器都会烧掉，懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.50,0:43:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.61,0:43:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}凝胶在哪一边？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.85,0:43:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}尝起来不错哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.13,0:43:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，把镜头调好，艾佛特！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.96,0:44:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这些纸留下好接回剪掉的底片
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.20,0:44:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}知道了，艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.04,0:44:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.04,0:44:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\1c&HC0C0C0&}《化身博士》 首映日期：1941年08月12日
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.42,0:44:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这给你用，今天你自己上卷轮
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.06,0:44:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.40,0:44:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你可以自己操作了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.33,0:44:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别动
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.34,0:44:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真美妙！换我了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.21,0:44:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}跟帕德瑞道别，他要去德国
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.09,0:45:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为什么不跟他说再见？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.96,0:45:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我爸说他是共产党
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.00,0:45:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上帝保佑你！妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.56,0:45:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他在德国真的能找到工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.03,0:45:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谁晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.27,0:45:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就像玩彩卷，凭运气罗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.44,0:45:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}去他的这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.01,0:45:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}到德国工作吧，史达林的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.28,0:45:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再见，妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.55,0:45:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再见，帕德瑞，快回来，再见
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.93,0:45:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}祝他在德国好运，那儿更靠近俄国
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.37,0:45:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}六年后大地回春，欣欣向荣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.07,0:45:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一扫战时夸张风格…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.99,0:46:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要把你们剁成肉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.10,0:46:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们给我走着瞧！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.12,0:46:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}情报单位公布之消息
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.46,0:46:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我国军民在俄国又一不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.26,0:46:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}国防部发布另一新的…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.33,0:46:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}意大利死亡名单，前此被视为…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.20,0:46:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}失踪姓名将由各地方军事当局公布
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.20,0:46:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}遗眷将会被通知
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.51,0:47:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然而，我们并不知他被埋在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.32,0:47:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这抚恤文件，请签名
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.32,0:48:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\shad5\1c&HC0C0C0&}《消防员》 首映日期：1949年04月16日
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.40,0:48:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有啊，他总是纠缠不休的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.91,0:49:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}回去吧，没有片子看了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.32,0:49:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}很晚了，请讲讲理，不可能重播
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.29,0:50:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有人坐着看两次
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.83,0:50:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们等了一个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.87,0:50:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}明天将上映西部片，我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.34,0:50:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一定是部精彩名作，回去睡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.25,0:50:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}哪有那么早就关门的！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.42,0:50:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们会把“天堂戏院”挤成地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.59,0:50:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}神父，开门哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.52,0:50:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，让我们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.26,0:50:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我能怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.70,0:50:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们已等了三个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.80,0:50:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“暴民不用大脑”
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.27,0:50:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“没有自我意志”
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}史宾塞崔西曾愤怒地这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.71,0:50:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这样子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.28,0:51:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们来让这些可怜人看到电影
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.92,0:51:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好啊，怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.06,0:51:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就算你不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.69,0:51:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也该信任你所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.30,0:51:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在，把屁股移开椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.97,0:51:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}准备，天灵灵，地灵灵
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.38,0:52:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们将它穿过墙
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.75,0:52:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}到窗外看看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.45,0:52:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.46,0:52:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们看！电影在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.87,0:52:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}太棒了，艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.03,0:52:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢你，艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.55,0:52:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}发生什么事？啊！是电影
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.52,0:52:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们这些人统统下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.47,0:53:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，没有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.80,0:53:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}该不该让他们快乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.67,0:53:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}应该
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.94,0:53:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要下去吗？去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.09,0:53:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老天，诺齐欧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.47,0:54:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}收半价
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.55,0:54:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要买票，各位，半价
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.96,0:54:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}少来，广场属于大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.59,0:54:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不，广场是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.76,0:54:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}少开这玩笑，简直要我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.10,0:57:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特！救命，谁来帮忙哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.03,0:57:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可怜的艾佛特，真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.03,0:58:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}全烧掉了，全烧得光溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.99,0:58:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么办才好？我们再也没有娱乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.16,0:58:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}哪来的钱可以重建？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.13,0:58:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你看是奇奇欧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.97,0:58:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}穿得如此光鲜叫人认不出
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.07,0:58:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谁有这样的钱来重建？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.92,0:58:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}新天堂戏院重新开张
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.76,0:59:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}请进
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.86,0:59:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}戏院为大家而开
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.10,0:59:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他只是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.44,0:59:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}儿童福利法怎么规定？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.90,0:59:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我透过关系拿到证明
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.07,0:59:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别问我他们怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.98,0:59:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}官方证明我是个放映师
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.11,0:59:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过薪水是给多多的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.82,0:59:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，好好做别再迷糊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.29,1:00:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}情况已够惨的了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.22,1:00:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}做艾佛特教你的事，愿上帝保佑你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.46,1:00:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢，神父
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.33,1:00:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么搞的？有死人哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.43,1:00:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}日子要快乐的过下去啊，音乐！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.93,1:00:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\1c&HC0C0C0&}《安娜》 首映日期：1951年12月20日
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.24,1:01:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你喜欢那个农夫吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.55,1:01:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.45,1:01:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是他吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.59,1:01:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不再爱我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.27,1:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好个女孩啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.07,1:02:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}天主保佑…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老天，他们在接吻
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.20,1:02:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我不看色情片
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.08,1:02:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为奇奇欧喝采
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.61,1:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}新天堂可有我容身之处
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.48,1:03:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.68,1:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，关门后带他回去，我走了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.72,1:03:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真高兴你能来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.43,1:03:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上课上得如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.70,1:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}很好，但我现在在工作
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.13,1:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}或许不再去上课了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.37,1:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不行，多多，不可这样
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.04,1:03:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}否则你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.21,1:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.08,1:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}意思是…这不是真正的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.06,1:04:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在天堂戏院需要你…你需要天堂
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.76,1:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但这只是暂时的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.10,1:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一天你会接触其他东西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.61,1:04:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}更重要的东西，相当重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.58,1:04:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}虽然我失去视力，但我看得更清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.49,1:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看到以前没看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.56,1:04:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢你救了我的命，我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.26,1:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别这副模样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.20,1:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我还没老呢，要证明吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.27,1:04:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.50,1:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我瞧瞧，例如…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.51,1:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在…影片焦距不对，检查一下
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.82,1:04:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没错，焦距模糊了，你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.09,1:05:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}难以解释
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.90,1:05:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只有一份拷贝？我需要二份
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.54,1:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一份给天堂戏院
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.17,1:05:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一份给邻镇的戏院，你答应的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.61,1:05:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我海报都贴出去了，非上映不可
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.41,1:05:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你敢耍我，给我小心一点
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.15,1:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一片两家戏院，你会付出代价的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.15,1:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我从那不勒斯来，你会死得很难看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.83,1:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老板，依我的看法…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.83,1:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}邻镇的电影院太过老旧了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.20,1:05:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.43,1:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}假若这部电影只映四天
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.60,1:05:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那倒不如放弃，电影院再重新装璜
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.94,1:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然后从市区调个放映师
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.88,1:05:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那么这部电影可分两楼放映
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.28,1:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你说的可容易
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.18,1:06:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我怎知事情会演变成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.35,1:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当初片商的预告只有一支拷贝
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.65,1:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是我拼了命跟他们争取
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.46,1:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且他们也答应了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.69,1:06:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那么第二支拷贝呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.19,1:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有了呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.19,1:06:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs10\bord0\pos(300,145)\frz360\1c&HC0C0C0&}《枷锁》 首映日期：1949年10月29日
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.90,1:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们到卧房看到小孩已睡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.88,1:07:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}罗莎！她的药在哪里？想办法呀
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.93,1:07:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}律师曾告诉我，现在，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.57,1:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}律师曾告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.24,1:07:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.44,1:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每个人一定都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.51,1:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每个人一定都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.38,1:07:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你相信我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.28,1:07:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你相信我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.05,1:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，我相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.39,1:07:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，我相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.43,1:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们自己的家，梦想许久的家
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.63,1:08:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们自己的家，梦想许久的家
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.98,1:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}托尼诺
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.41,1:08:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}托尼诺
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.48,1:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.08,1:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.97,1:08:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}剧终
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.72,1:08:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.63,1:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我把片尾名单剪掉以节省时间
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.06,1:09:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}倒回上集，我来播新闻片
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.80,1:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要报警抓走他，他已经看十遍了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.07,1:09:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}等等，等等…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.36,1:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}波其亚，下集给我，这是上集
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.97,1:09:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快，戏院爆满了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.17,1:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快呀，别再拖了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.00,1:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}让它转！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.74,1:09:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一堆动物，安静
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.41,1:10:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}管他的！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.89,1:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，搞什么鬼！到现在还不放
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.93,1:10:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快呀，多多！他们快爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.16,1:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}都已经过半小时了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.50,1:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我能怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.44,1:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那个驴儿子呢？我完蛋了，安静…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.54,1:10:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我必须立刻看到这部电影
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.98,1:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我丢下老婆一人卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.85,1:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而我却什么也没看到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.49,1:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}十分钟内不放映
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.52,1:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}把钱还来，大家散会
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.53,1:11:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}否则，我把这儿拆了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.17,1:11:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静…请听我说
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.81,1:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}告诉各位，我改天再映上集
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.28,1:11:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看来得结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.68,1:11:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}安静！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.75,1:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我看过整部电影，我告诉你们剧情
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.56,1:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}波其亚，波其亚你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.60,1:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.57,1:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好爽！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.07,1:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}走开！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.34,1:12:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好爽呐！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.04,1:12:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\1c&HD0D0D0&}《上帝创造女人》 首映日期：1956年11月28日
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.60,1:13:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们在干什么？专心看电影
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.17,1:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他妈的！畜生，看电影
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.84,1:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我告诉过你，它不会着火
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.12,1:14:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}进步总是来得太迟
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.69,1:14:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0}《七对佳偶》 首映日期：1955年07月21日
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.81,1:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}各位！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.00,1:15:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}小伙子…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.71,1:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}裤子脱掉，多多，没啥好怕的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.38,1:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是，我怕会流血
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.32,1:15:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}流血？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.12,1:15:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你这个傻蛋，上来，不用怕
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.43,1:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么样，什么也没有吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.40,1:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}对，就是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.38,1:16:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喔，你真是个英俊的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.57,1:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“车站”
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.53,1:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她是新来的，长得不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.84,1:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}感觉蛮随和的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.21,1:17:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她爸是银行经理，骄傲又目中无人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.28,1:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}总是身穿毕挺衣服，光洁整齐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.82,1:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}加油！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.10,1:17:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}对不起，你掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.05,1:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢！我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.32,1:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我叫沙维图迪维多，你呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.06,1:17:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:17:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我想告诉你…前几天在火车站…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.93,1:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是“摩登时代”这部片子吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.87,1:18:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.61,1:18:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}经典名片是不可能被遗忘的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.88,1:18:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}40年前放这部片子时
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.91,1:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我的前妻死了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.38,1:18:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是在下了班才知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.89,1:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是最后一个知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.89,1:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当时，吓了一跳，永远也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.93,1:18:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}小放映师，是你拍的底片吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.94,1:18:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的 拍了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.01,1:18:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}屠夫，正在杀小牛
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.18,1:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}地面上沾满了血渍
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.95,1:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}湖边是另一头小牛，即将毙命
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.06,1:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为何停下来？看到什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.09,1:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，没什么，一片茫然
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.57,1:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}女人？是女人对吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.97,1:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，一位在车站遇到的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.61,1:19:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么模样？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.58,1:19:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}很漂亮，跟我同年龄，纤瘦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.09,1:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}金色长发，蓝色的眼珠，好纯真
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.99,1:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}嘴唇上有颗小美人痣，很小
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.56,1:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}靠近时才能看见
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.50,1:19:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她笑时让人觉得…难以形容
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.60,1:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}恋爱
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.77,1:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我知道是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.15,1:19:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}蓝眸子的人最坏，不论你做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.35,1:20:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她都不会当你是朋友，绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.46,1:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}人长愈大，印象愈深
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.36,1:20:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}若谈没有结局的恋爱是会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.00,1:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你刚说的很美好，但很悲观
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.14,1:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不是我说的，是约翰韦恩说的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.28,1:20:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你这老头
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.16,1:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.06,1:21:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你为何用跑的？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.16,1:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}因为…我想…告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.30,1:21:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你可记得当我们…今天天气真好
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.72,1:21:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是啊，真的很好
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.45,1:21:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}抱歉，我得走了，再见
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.16,1:21:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我真驴…“天气真好”驴死了！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.18,1:22:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是你永远的终身伴侣
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.45,1:22:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这可不是马龙白兰度说的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.59,1:22:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你觉得我长得怎么样？丑吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.13,1:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}亲爱的艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.20,1:22:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这次我表现得好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.11,1:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喂！请问艾琳娜在吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.45,1:22:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}美琳娜，对不起，大概你不记得了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.72,1:22:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是沙维图迪多
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.92,1:22:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就是经常和你无意中碰面的那个
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.72,1:22:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每当和你见面
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.19,1:22:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}心中总是高兴得说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.46,1:22:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}昨晚，想了一夜要对你说
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.67,1:23:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你总是让我朝思暮想，我好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.34,1:23:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你再说，我叫警察来抓你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.14,1:23:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.18,1:23:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是艾琳娜的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.55,1:23:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}对不起！我不知道你是…我的天！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.95,1:23:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我告诉过你，你却当成耳边风
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.43,1:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}记住我的话，蓝眸子的人最坏
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.86,1:23:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为什么，一定有办法让她明白
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.30,1:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别尝试了，多多
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.37,1:23:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}感情之事难以了解，也难以解释
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.34,1:23:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别再像个教士般地说教
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.48,1:23:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你可以停止了！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.48,1:23:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，听我说，别生气
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.52,1:23:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是为你好才这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.35,1:23:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}借过，别挡在路中央
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.49,1:24:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多！你在哪里？他真的生气走了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.81,1:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你要像我的孩子陪着我，听到没？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.88,1:24:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要尊敬上帝
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.75,1:24:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他在2、3天内创造世界
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.75,1:24:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我花的时间久一些
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.22,1:24:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但我很谦虚，我愿做得更好一些
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.39,1:24:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我常说：他总有答案
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.56,1:24:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那只是对你，多多，我讲个故事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.23,1:24:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}先坐下来，悲剧中的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.28,1:24:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一次，国王为美丽的公主开宴会
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.35,1:24:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有个士兵在一旁站岗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.39,1:24:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看到公主经过他面前
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.79,1:25:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她是绝色佳人，他立刻爱上她
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.80,1:25:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但卑微的士兵
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.56,1:25:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎配得上国王的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.47,1:25:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一天，他终于设法接近她
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.27,1:25:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}并告诉她没有她活不下去
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.81,1:25:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}公主被他的深情感动，她告诉士兵
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.38,1:25:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“如果你能等我100天”
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.49,1:25:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}且日日夜夜在阳台下等我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.99,1:25:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}百日之后“ ”我就是你的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.59,1:25:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听了这话，士兵在阳台下等
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.93,1:25:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一天、二天、十天、二十天
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.97,1:25:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}公主每晚往外探，他仍伫立终宵
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.58,1:25:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}风雪雨都抵挡不了他
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.68,1:26:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}鸟停在头上，蜜蜂叮他，他都不动
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.32,1:26:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但是…在第九十天时
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.36,1:26:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}士兵全身已…苍白且瘦削
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.60,1:26:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}眼泪从眼眶里流了出来
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.51,1:26:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他已支撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.64,1:26:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}甚至连睡觉的力气都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.21,1:26:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}公主一直注视着他
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.35,1:26:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}最后，在第九十九天的晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.22,1:26:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}士兵站了起来
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.19,1:26:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}提起椅子，走了！走了！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.76,1:26:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}结局竟是这样？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.50,1:26:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.70,1:26:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}无言的结局
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.20,1:26:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别问是什么意思，我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.91,1:27:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果你知道，就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.44,1:28:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，帮我一个忙…留住神父
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.59,1:28:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，什么事？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.29,1:28:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不行，我得听告解
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.36,1:28:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}神父，我急需要你！因为…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.07,1:28:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我有些疑问
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.80,1:28:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这个疑问困扰我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.87,1:28:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你的灵魂？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.01,1:28:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}神父，我有罪…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.42,1:28:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}待会再说！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.45,1:28:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.45,1:28:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}待着别走，保持正常
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.02,1:28:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是沙维图迪维多
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.76,1:28:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你怎么在这？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.33,1:29:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特，这真是件可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.10,1:29:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我知道，这是…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.67,1:29:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现世利益的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.50,1:29:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎样，说下去呀，好可怕
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.77,1:29:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我怀疑，这可能吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.57,1:29:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我母亲已对我爸说了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.84,1:29:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}难道你连我的声音都听不出来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.32,1:29:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}对不起！我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.05,1:29:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过我还是得和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.63,1:29:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你好美，艾琳娜，我一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.93,1:29:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看到你时，我说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.40,1:29:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你让我发抖…简直令我手足无措
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.95,1:29:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是我的初恋，我已爱上你了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.45,1:30:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}神父，我有罪
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.36,1:30:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我以父，子及圣灵之名赦你无罪
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.67,1:30:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当你笑时，更迷人了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.38,1:30:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图迪维多，你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.51,1:30:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我很喜欢你，但并不代表我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.42,1:30:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不管怎样，我愿意等
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.19,1:30:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.42,1:30:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}等你也爱上我，听着
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.13,1:30:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每晚我下班后会站在你家外面等你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.04,1:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}若你改变心意
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.91,1:30:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}请打开窗子就可以了，我明白
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.11,1:30:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你清楚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.41,1:31:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是的，我终于看到亮光
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.42,1:31:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}下次别在这里说，虽然你浩劫余生
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.22,1:31:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但能否逃过永恒之火…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.56,1:31:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}永恒之火是无人能救的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.99,1:32:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多也真是的，电影应该结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.55,1:33:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快到了，再15秒就是新年了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.15,1:33:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}11秒…10秒…9秒…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.16,1:33:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}5秒…4秒…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.10,1:33:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不用担心，他一定和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.87,1:33:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}来！干杯
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.94,1:33:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}新年快乐！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.71,1:33:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}新年快乐！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.31,1:33:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也为多多干杯
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.68,1:35:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图迪维多！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.40,1:37:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}老天，我从来没有开过车
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.18,1:37:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们怎么回去？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.18,1:37:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}停车
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.82,1:37:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}糟了，是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.19,1:37:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}门多拉先生，你好
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.54,1:37:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你好！你好！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.97,1:37:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.41,1:37:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}欢迎您欣赏“二倍猜谜”的节目
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.85,1:37:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}让我们欢迎主持人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.49,1:37:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.46,1:38:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有底片怎么放出影像？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.83,1:38:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是电视，可以不用底片
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.37,1:38:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且您也可以买来在家里看
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.37,1:38:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}才不！我讨厌那个烧焦的臭味
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.22,1:38:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这部机器是租来的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.99,1:38:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过，若为了戏院的生意
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.49,1:38:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真需要买台新的电视放映机
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.56,1:38:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}来充实戏院的设备
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.47,1:38:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}答案是但丁的“神曲”
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.58,1:38:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你父亲是不是讨厌我的工作？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.39,1:38:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还是嫌我们家穷？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.39,1:38:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.42,1:39:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我爸妈暑假要去别的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.03,1:39:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那时我们再见面
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.37,1:39:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是，我夏天要去郊外放电影
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.50,1:39:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.04,1:39:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那我每天写信给你，我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.44,1:39:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}记得夏天如果结束要赶快回来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.98,1:39:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.60,1:39:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“户外电影院即将开业”
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.95,1:40:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只剩站票，进去不要钱，出来再付
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.36,1:40:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}请进，才刚开始，票准备好
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.27,1:40:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图，我的爱
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.04,1:40:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}整个夏天都和家人在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.04,1:40:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有你的日子毫无生趣
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.04,1:40:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}到处浮现你的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.37,1:40:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}看书时，猜字谜时，看报时
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.68,1:41:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}处处皆是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.01,1:41:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}今天有个坏消息，十月份
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.08,1:41:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我家搬到巴勒摩，将在那念大学
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.09,1:41:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以我们不能日夜厮守
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.65,1:41:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但请放心，只要有机会
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.39,1:41:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我便会奔向“天堂”找你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.65,1:41:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你们谁来帮我开门
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.61,1:42:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么每天都有你的信？有够烦的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.35,1:42:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}嫉妒还是羡慕？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.50,1:42:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\1c&HD7D7D7&}《尤利西斯》 首映日期：1954年10月06日
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.74,1:42:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.65,1:42:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.26,1:43:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这个烂夏天何时结束？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.86,1:43:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在电影里，它早已结束
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.83,1:43:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}此刻若来阵暴风雨一定很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.39,1:43:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“告诉他们我是奥狄赛”
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.53,1:44:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜，你何时回来？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.84,1:44:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}今天，你绝猜不到我来这里的借口
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.51,1:44:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}苏菲亚罗兰依旧是那样
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.64,1:44:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有修长的腿，丰满的胸脯…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.92,1:45:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}戏院老板，多多的信
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.99,1:45:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}转交给他
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.85,1:45:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.39,1:45:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}天哪！怎么办？怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.87,1:45:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}市公所有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.67,1:45:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我父亲是战死的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.30,1:45:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我应该免除兵役才对
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.01,1:45:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可能他们弄错了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.61,1:45:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}星期五在罗马报到
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.31,1:45:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}放心，我十天就退伍了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.41,1:45:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}走吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.41,1:45:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不！我今天要回去，我爸来接我了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.62,1:45:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么那么巧，我还有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.29,1:45:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}告诉你，今天我有个约会
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.39,1:45:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}跟谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.76,1:45:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是我爸同事的孩子，以后再聊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.43,1:45:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我星期四搭五点的公车来找你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.64,1:45:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你等我！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.46,1:46:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\shad0\3a&H28&}今天上映《旁徨》
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.00,1:46:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs26\bord0\shad5\4a&HFF&\pos(198,245)\1c&HD9D9D9&}导演：米开兰基罗，安东尼奥尼
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.80,1:46:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs26\bord0\shad5\4a&HFF&\pos(198,200)\1c&HD4D4D4&}主演：阿莉达华丽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.71,1:46:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，或许是陆军搞错了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.82,1:46:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}明天将卷轮装上准备给新人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.95,1:46:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}知道了！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.96,1:46:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}开心点，我会等你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.36,1:46:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别担心，工作仍是你的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.43,1:46:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我会等，听到没？不要愁眉苦脸
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.10,1:48:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你在等人吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.17,1:48:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，我是下来接你的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.50,1:48:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}少装了，是不是在等女朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.97,1:48:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你要一个人在这里等
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.84,1:48:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还是我和你一起等
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.08,1:48:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我看我不在这儿会比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.98,1:48:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不，我要你帮我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.84,1:48:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听，声音…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.54,1:48:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\1c&HEFEFEF&}《浪荡儿》 首映日期：1953年09月17日
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.51,1:49:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}开门！
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.19,1:49:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}开门！艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.09,1:49:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPLiJinHeiW8-GB\fs20\bord0\4a&HC7&\1c&HD8D8D8&}《呐喊》 首映日期：1957年06月22日
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.02,1:50:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}气死我了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.94,1:50:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，你去哪儿？去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.11,1:50:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别担心，坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.62,1:50:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.76,1:50:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.62,1:51:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}第九团，第三营
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.92,1:51:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}通信兵沙维图迪维多报到
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.09,1:51:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我的退伍令下来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.76,1:51:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还没有接到通知
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.14,1:51:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她爸将她转学了，不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.77,1:51:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有人知道她转去哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.85,1:51:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不告诉我，我打烂你的头，混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.19,1:51:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}查无此人
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.07,1:51:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我应该只当十天兵的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.00,1:52:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么会变成一年，而且都没有休假
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.70,1:52:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你的退伍令已经下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.94,1:54:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你瘦了，终于退伍了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.31,1:54:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听说你从不出门
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.11,1:54:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也不和人说话，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.22,1:54:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你知道原因，这是迟早的事
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.12,1:54:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不论你说不说都不会改变事实
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.23,1:54:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以你最好闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.84,1:54:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这里好热，带我去看海
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.98,1:54:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在个舞会上
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.24,1:54:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有个中尉掐一个女孩子的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.85,1:54:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}她转过身才知道是团长的女儿
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.32,1:55:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}中尉吃惊的说：
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.15,1:55:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果你的心也像你的屁股一样硬
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.56,1:55:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那我就死定了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.66,1:55:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你有她的消息吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.00,1:55:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，没有人知道她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.24,1:55:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}或许这是上天安排的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.38,1:55:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每个人都只是在追逐一颗星星
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.38,1:55:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在，你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.43,1:55:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一次，司令官对军官说
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.40,1:55:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那边有一座风车
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.04,1:56:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}军官回答：风车是没有，不过有风
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.62,1:56:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你告诉我的故事还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.24,1:56:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我知道士兵为何会那么做
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.05,1:56:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}因为他明白，如果在一百天时
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.02,1:56:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}公主不承认她的约定，那么
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.09,1:56:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}士兵将会伤心难过，绝望的死去
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.43,1:56:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以他选择在99天的夜晚离去
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.70,1:56:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这样公主将会永远惦记着他
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.67,1:57:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}跟士兵一样，多多，离开这里…
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.57,1:57:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这地方给下咒了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.64,1:57:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}日复一日生活在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.28,1:57:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你会以为这里就是世界中心
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.05,1:57:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}事情不会有任何改变的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.72,1:57:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但如果你离开一两年后
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.69,1:57:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再回来时，每件事都会改变
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.03,1:57:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}线也断了，你会发现人事全非
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.17,1:57:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}属于你的都已消失
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.01,1:57:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你必须离开这里一段时间
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.17,1:57:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}直到你有所成再回来看看亲友
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.15,1:57:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}回到这个你出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.05,1:57:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在不行，不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.22,1:57:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你此刻比我还瞎
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.22,1:57:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是谁说的？贾利古柏？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.22,1:57:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}詹母史都华？亨利方达？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.53,1:58:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不，多多，这不是什么台词
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.53,1:58:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这次是我的真心话
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.17,1:58:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}生活和电影不一样，生活难多了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.24,1:58:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}离开这里去罗马吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.85,1:58:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你如此年轻，世界是你的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.69,1:58:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而我老了，我不要再听你的说话
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.69,1:58:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我要听别人谈论你
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.46,2:00:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不准回来，不准想我们
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.79,2:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不准回头，不准写信
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.70,2:00:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不准妥协，忘了我们
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.30,2:00:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果你办不到回来了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.84,2:00:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是不会让你进我屋子的，明白吗
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.68,2:00:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我明白，谢谢你为我做的一切
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.56,2:00:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不论你做什么工作，要去爱它
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.33,2:00:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就像你爱放映机一样
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.23,2:00:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当时你真是个小淘气
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.21,2:01:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}来迟了，多多！再见！
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.88,2:01:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，再见
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.85,2:01:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多！
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.26,2:01:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}来晚了点，真可惜
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.32,2:02:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是多多，我知道是他
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.44,2:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.99,2:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你的妹妹他们过得很好
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.82,2:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}孩子也都长大了
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.93,2:03:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我常接到她的信，看这房子多棒
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.37,2:03:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}重新整修过，全都得谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.37,2:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我有个惊喜给你，来
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.88,2:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}累吗？葬礼前可先休息一下
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.35,2:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不！妈妈，我搭一小时后的飞机
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.09,2:03:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}离开30年了，不能说走就走
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.56,2:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}来，我把你的东西全放在这里
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.07,2:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他一定很高兴你回来，多多
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.61,2:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他总是谈你，总是谈你
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.18,2:05:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}甚至到最后一口气仍是
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.88,2:05:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他真的很爱你
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.90,2:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他留了一些东西给你
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.54,2:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在你离开之前，记得来我家
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.70,2:07:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你好
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.15,2:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}何时关闭的？
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.12,2:07:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}6年前5月，再也没人来看了
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.69,2:07:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你比我清楚，沙维图迪维多先生
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.26,2:07:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}经济因素，有了电视
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.76,2:07:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}录影带，电影已变成回忆
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.90,2:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}市政府买下来作为停车场
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.30,2:08:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}星期六就要将它炸毁，真可悲
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.17,2:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}为何叫沙维图迪维多先生？
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.28,2:08:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你过去常使唤我
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.31,2:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你现在是大人物…总是有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.18,2:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但如果你坚持，我仍叫你多多
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.03,2:08:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}失陪
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.87,2:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}真不敢相信，小多多
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.50,2:09:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我们和外婆想去罗马玩
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.17,2:09:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}顺便看一下舅舅的工作
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.01,2:09:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好哇，不过不要抱太大的希望
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.08,2:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}因为我的工作是很无聊的喔！
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.82,2:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}大哥，这点你大可放心
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.85,2:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们可都是你忠实的观众
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.79,2:09:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}明天出发吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.86,2:09:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不知道，我还没决定
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.35,2:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们已打了好几通电话来
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.76,2:10:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}问你什么时候回去
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.29,2:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}麻烦给我一杯威士忌
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.97,2:13:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}请问你是导演沙维图先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.18,2:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}能否给我签个名，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.45,2:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}对不起，我想我认错人了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.18,2:16:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你要常打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.21,2:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你不来送我，那我以后就不理你了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:42.45,2:16:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.19,2:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}好吧！我走了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.87,2:17:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么了？多多
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.68,2:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有些话一直没有对您说…
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.35,2:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}小时候您辛苦抚养我们
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.29,2:17:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在我们长大了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.69,2:18:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}却都不在您身边奉养您
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.94,2:18:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一点我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,2:18:14.04,2:18:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}您年轻的时候那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.88,2:18:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}应该有个美好的人生
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.25,2:18:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是您为何选择孤独的生活？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.69,2:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是人都会有感情…您为何不再婚？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.64,2:18:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}难道您没想过吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.08,2:18:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}以前一直没留意这件事
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.48,2:18:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如今想来真是不应该
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.42,2:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那个时候根本不敢奢望会再有恋人
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.76,2:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}始终我只爱你父亲一个人
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.73,2:19:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这样的个性是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.76,2:19:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我和你一样
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.30,2:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}非常珍惜自己喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.74,2:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过说真的…
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.44,2:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}从一而终内心虽是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.44,2:19:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但却活得很踏实
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.45,2:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们又在催你回去了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.46,2:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}别管他们了，妈妈
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.99,2:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}说真的…我一直好怕回来
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.90,2:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}过了这么多年，我以为…坚强多了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.77,2:19:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也以为已忘了这一切
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.91,2:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如今回来才知道我们是属于这里
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.85,2:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}感觉仿佛未曾离开过
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.99,2:20:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然而，妹妹看我却像个陌生人
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.06,2:20:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而您，妈妈，我遗弃您
Dialogue: 0,2:20:16.40,2:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}像个强盗般地远离您
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.84,2:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有一句解释
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.70,2:20:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我从未要求，你也无需解释
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.01,2:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我一直认为你做的是对的
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.81,2:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}何必去追究，想想过去
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.65,2:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每天晚上，睡觉前关大门的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.52,2:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}总是没将钥匙锁上
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.66,2:20:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}以前不是没有钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.46,2:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那时你在电影院工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.87,2:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在你没回家前，其实我都没有入睡
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.54,2:20:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一直到你回来
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.78,2:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我在房中听到你进寝室的声音
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.21,2:21:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}确定你睡了我才偷偷的起来
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.88,2:21:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}将大门锁上
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.42,2:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}自从你离开这里后
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.96,2:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我还是将钥匙挂在门上
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.56,2:21:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就怕你回来时，门锁着进不来
Dialogue: 0,2:21:24.97,2:21:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这种心情…
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.60,2:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}然而你离开这里是对的
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.94,2:21:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你已实现自己的理想
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.98,2:21:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每次打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,2:21:37.78,2:21:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}总是有不同的女人接
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.62,2:21:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我自己常这么想
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.49,2:21:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}大概那些女人都不是你喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.96,2:21:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这只不过是我自己胡乱猜想的
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.56,2:21:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是…
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.00,2:22:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我听不出其中有哪个是真心爱你的
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.67,2:22:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有的时候，我想看你…
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.21,2:22:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}能安定下来，专心爱一个人
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.68,2:22:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但你人在远处
Dialogue: 0,2:22:14.95,2:22:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这里只剩鬼魂，忘了她吧，多多
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.85,2:23:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}波其亚？
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.70,2:23:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}本名是…理承诺
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.37,2:23:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喂！
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.80,2:24:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喂！请问你是艾琳娜吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.73,2:24:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我是，哪位？
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.07,2:24:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图，我是沙维图迪维多
Dialogue: 0,2:25:00.98,2:25:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.96,2:25:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我就在你家前的电话亭
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.48,2:25:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我记起来了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:33.32,2:25:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可以下来见个面吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.16,2:25:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那都是过去式了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.89,2:25:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在见面有什么用？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.86,2:25:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我只想见你一面，你我年纪都大了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.87,2:25:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还是不要见面比较好，再见
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.31,2:26:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}喂！
Dialogue: 0,2:27:36.11,2:27:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图迪维多
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.64,2:28:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你怎么知道我在这？
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.14,2:28:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我知道你以前最喜欢来海边
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.31,2:28:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以我就来这儿…找你
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.57,2:28:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你还是那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:28:49.18,2:28:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}少来了，都已经老了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:58.02,2:29:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你还看不出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:29:04.19,2:29:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你怎么会回来的？
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.53,2:29:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特死了，你还记得他吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.44,2:29:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当然记得
Dialogue: 0,2:29:16.20,2:29:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我很难过，他对你那么好
Dialogue: 0,2:29:25.41,2:29:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我见到你的女儿了，长得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.92,2:29:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}追她的人一定很多吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.23,2:29:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是啊！还有一些人你没见过
Dialogue: 0,2:29:47.07,2:29:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我还有个男孩，他是老大，你呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.64,2:30:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，我还没结婚，幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.09,2:30:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还好，过去只不过是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,2:30:14.10,2:30:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你知道我先生是谁？
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.40,2:30:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}理承诺、波其亚，我知道
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.04,2:30:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他现在从事什么性质工作？
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.11,2:30:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有关政治的，县议会的议员
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.25,2:30:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是大学时候的同学
Dialogue: 0,2:30:42.12,2:30:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你父亲同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.49,2:30:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，父亲仍是反对
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.10,2:30:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你一直在等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.51,2:31:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我一直没有忘记你
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.15,2:31:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我也是，为何你突然失去踪影？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:18.66,2:31:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}现在说这些也没有用了
Dialogue: 0,2:31:27.14,2:31:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在你面前流泪只会让你觉得好笑
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.07,2:31:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一直在罗马吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:32.71,2:31:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你说这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:35.38,2:31:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}电影院的约定你为何没去？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:39.18,2:31:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而你却连一句话也不说就离开
Dialogue: 0,2:31:41.25,2:31:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你知道我已经等你三十年了
Dialogue: 0,2:31:53.70,2:31:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}电影院的约定我去了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.64,2:32:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只是我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.71,2:32:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我爸妈为了我们的事大吵一架
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.08,2:32:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我想尽办法说服他们，但没有用
Dialogue: 0,2:32:19.59,2:32:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们仍然…决定要搬离这里
Dialogue: 0,2:32:27.36,2:32:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}而且当晚就要离开
Dialogue: 0,2:32:32.57,2:32:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我很着急，不晓得该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,2:32:42.14,2:32:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}最后在我苦苦哀求下…
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.59,2:32:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他们才答应让我见你最后一面
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.86,2:33:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我打算…只要能跟你见面…
Dialogue: 0,2:33:02.86,2:33:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那我俩就可以…一起私奔！
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.15,2:33:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是到了电影院时
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.22,2:33:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只有艾佛特在那儿
Dialogue: 0,2:33:27.52,2:33:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我根本没有多少时间等你
Dialogue: 0,2:33:33.60,2:33:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}快一点，艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,2:33:35.46,2:33:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以我只好告诉艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,2:33:38.53,2:33:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我将在今晚离开
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.24,2:33:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}要他转告给你我说的话
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.37,2:33:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他很亲切
Dialogue: 0,2:33:49.38,2:33:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}且很诚恳的在听我说话…
Dialogue: 0,2:33:55.65,2:33:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你先冷静下来…
Dialogue: 0,2:34:00.99,2:34:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}听我说，多多要我告诉你…
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.90,2:34:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他认为你们俩分开会比较好
Dialogue: 0,2:34:11.37,2:34:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他是为了你才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.34,2:34:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不要难过，他不是有意的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:20.68,2:34:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}火烧完了剩下来的只有灰烬
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.88,2:34:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}恋情是否能持续谁也无法预料
Dialogue: 0,2:34:27.92,2:34:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以他不想再维持这段恋情
Dialogue: 0,2:34:32.39,2:34:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多的将来是他自己能决定的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:36.02,2:34:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}既然他这么说，我也无法再说什么
Dialogue: 0,2:34:40.30,2:34:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我也想不透他竟然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,2:34:44.53,2:34:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不过你要了解他的用意
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.37,2:34:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}离开他，照他的意思做
Dialogue: 0,2:35:11.29,2:35:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你是否明天就要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,2:35:22.77,2:35:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特怎么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,2:35:27.44,2:35:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}难道你相信他的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:35:31.81,2:35:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我只是暂且顺着他的意思
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.78,2:35:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我还有留一张字条给你
Dialogue: 0,2:35:48.93,2:35:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}当我在下楼梯时
Dialogue: 0,2:35:52.97,2:35:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}想到他眼睛是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,2:35:58.34,2:36:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我就转身回放映室
Dialogue: 0,2:36:02.58,2:36:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他默默的坐在放影机前
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.35,2:36:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我拿起挂在墙壁上的纸
Dialogue: 0,2:36:13.32,2:36:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}写我的地址
Dialogue: 0,2:36:18.46,2:36:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“我等你的消息”…
Dialogue: 0,2:36:24.80,2:36:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}可是你却从此消失无踪
Dialogue: 0,2:36:37.81,2:36:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我到处打听你的消息
Dialogue: 0,2:36:43.15,2:36:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但都无着落
Dialogue: 0,2:36:46.72,2:36:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我写信，打电话
Dialogue: 0,2:36:51.49,2:36:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}也都连络不到你
Dialogue: 0,2:36:57.67,2:37:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}所以我才离开这里
Dialogue: 0,2:37:03.84,2:37:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,2:37:08.84,2:37:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我也只能在梦里和你相见
Dialogue: 0,2:37:23.49,2:37:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}时间过得真快…
Dialogue: 0,2:37:26.43,2:37:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我见过很多好女孩
Dialogue: 0,2:37:29.40,2:37:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但我一直忘不了你
Dialogue: 0,2:37:33.40,2:37:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}虽然我的事业已有所成就
Dialogue: 0,2:37:41.71,2:37:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但我仍无时无刻在想念着你
Dialogue: 0,2:37:47.48,2:37:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就像小时候我盼望父亲回来一样
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.89,2:37:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你也是那样让我感到…
Dialogue: 0,2:37:58.56,2:38:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}心碎
Dialogue: 0,2:38:00.86,2:38:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}起初我也无法谅解艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,2:38:05.23,2:38:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}但经过这么多年…
Dialogue: 0,2:38:08.47,2:38:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我已能明白他当时的做法
Dialogue: 0,2:38:12.71,2:38:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他的沉默也已意味着对他的谅解
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.08,2:38:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你的留言我没有看到
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.58,2:38:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}时事都已境迁，那张纸也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,2:38:25.62,2:38:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}还在不在，也许早被丢掉了…
Dialogue: 0,2:38:29.46,2:38:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那已无关紧要，别再想它了
Dialogue: 0,2:38:33.80,2:38:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}事情都已过去了
Dialogue: 0,2:38:37.00,2:38:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾佛特之所以不告诉你真相
Dialogue: 0,2:38:39.60,2:38:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你应当是最能感受他这番苦心的
Dialogue: 0,2:38:43.47,2:38:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}想想，如果当时我们结了婚
Dialogue: 0,2:38:47.74,2:38:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}那你就不会制作出那么多好电影
Dialogue: 0,2:38:51.51,2:38:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你所拍的电影我每部都有看
Dialogue: 0,2:38:58.22,2:39:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只是，你没有用你的名字…
Dialogue: 0,2:39:02.52,2:39:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你应该用你的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:39:05.63,2:39:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}沙维图迪维多
Dialogue: 0,2:40:19.83,2:40:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是他留给你的
Dialogue: 0,2:40:37.12,2:40:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}每次电视播出你的影片
Dialogue: 0,2:40:42.86,2:40:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他都很高兴
Dialogue: 0,2:40:46.06,2:40:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他总是在电视机前坐着
Dialogue: 0,2:40:48.33,2:40:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}你的所有影片他都记得
Dialogue: 0,2:40:53.64,2:40:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我一边解说，他一边听着
Dialogue: 0,2:40:57.14,2:41:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}甚至连你的新闻他都不会错过
Dialogue: 0,2:41:03.88,2:41:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一遍两遍重覆地念着
Dialogue: 0,2:41:11.35,2:41:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他从没要求要见我一面？
Dialogue: 0,2:41:13.12,2:41:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}没有，从来没有
Dialogue: 0,2:41:17.73,2:41:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}有一次，令堂对他说
Dialogue: 0,2:41:20.73,2:41:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}如果他想见你，你一定会赶来
Dialogue: 0,2:41:25.33,2:41:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他好生气
Dialogue: 0,2:41:27.14,2:41:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他说：不行
Dialogue: 0,2:41:29.30,2:41:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}多多不可以回来这里
Dialogue: 0,2:41:35.81,2:41:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他没有恶意，他是个好人
Dialogue: 0,2:41:41.75,2:41:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谁知他说这些话时脑袋在想什么
Dialogue: 0,2:41:45.82,2:41:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他临终时说了些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,2:41:52.66,2:41:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}就连阖眼的那一杀那
Dialogue: 0,2:41:56.77,2:42:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}他还要你母亲不可以让你知道
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.88,2:42:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}在哪里？到底在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.51,2:42:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“白鲸记”
Dialogue: 0,2:42:48.75,2:42:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“抽履里的梦”
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.72,2:42:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“挑战”
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.99,2:42:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“野生之道”
Dialogue: 0,2:42:59.86,2:43:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“妄执”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.37,2:43:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“旁徨”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:18.45,2:43:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“沙维图迪维多…”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:21.38,2:43:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“对不起”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:24.95,2:43:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“这件事以后再跟你解释”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:28.32,2:43:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“先告诉你件很不好的消息”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:31.89,2:43:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“今天，母亲坚持要离开这里”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:36.50,2:43:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“而且今晚就要搬家”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.97,2:43:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“我只爱你一个人”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:41.90,2:43:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“我发誓今生今世绝不会变心”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:51.11,2:43:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“我留下朋友的地址记得要来信”
Dialogue: 0,2:43:58.05,2:44:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“我永远爱你”
Dialogue: 0,2:44:02.92,2:44:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“再见”
Dialogue: 0,2:44:06.53,2:44:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}“你的艾琳娜”
Dialogue: 0,2:44:12.87,2:44:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么时候离开？
Dialogue: 0,2:44:16.00,2:44:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}今天下午
Dialogue: 0,2:44:19.17,2:44:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}艾琳娜
Dialogue: 0,2:44:21.48,2:44:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}将来，我们…
Dialogue: 0,2:44:23.24,2:44:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不，没有将来了
Dialogue: 0,2:44:26.28,2:44:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}只有过去
Dialogue: 0,2:44:29.85,2:44:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}昨晚只是一场梦而已
Dialogue: 0,2:44:33.15,2:44:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}一个美好的梦
Dialogue: 0,2:44:37.36,2:44:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}是我们小时候没实现的梦…
Dialogue: 0,2:44:41.36,2:44:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:44:45.37,2:44:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我想，没有比这样更好的结局了
Dialogue: 0,2:44:55.98,2:44:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我不会这么想的
Dialogue: 0,2:44:59.65,2:45:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}绝对不会…
Dialogue: 0,2:46:44.45,2:46:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}这是我的广场
Dialogue: 0,2:47:12.65,2:47:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}检查底片，准备好时就放
Dialogue: 0,2:47:15.68,2:47:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我喜欢你的片子，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,2:47:18.99,2:47:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:21.09,2:47:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}什么事？
Dialogue: 0,2:47:22.09,2:47:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}上午新片发表
Dialogue: 0,2:47:23.62,2:47:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}下午召开记者会
Dialogue: 0,2:47:26.79,2:47:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}演员及制片均要出席
Dialogue: 0,2:47:29.36,2:47:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}刚才接到得奖通知…
Dialogue: 0,2:47:31.67,2:47:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}贺电已堆积如山了
Dialogue: 0,2:47:35.34,2:47:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}怎么，你不高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.01,2:47:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs22\3a&H28&}我当然高兴，待会再说吧！

